    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/7f51ecae34c69e402fb82dc13e4f5730.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/dc7841a521a9c937fc55f267ec39d0b8.poster.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/dc7841a521a9c937fc55f267ec39d0b8.webm?t=1749380861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/c204ccfd6254b22e2c57ec7f0f9616d5.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/6003a6a0e66c608575534b10818840bd.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在经历多年的云游生活之后，孤身一人的旅行者终于回到了自己的故乡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与青梅竹马重逢后，两人前往了村子里的洞窟调查魔物出没的缘由，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那里，有一个神秘的声音告诉他——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界已经陷入了危机，而只有他才能化险为夷，拯救这个世界……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这部游戏中，您需要穿越整个大陆，消灭阴谋集团的爪牙，探索被隐藏的故事与真相，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您究竟能否赶在帝国对散布在大陆各处的水晶动手前，将这些水晶保护起来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而一直出现在您耳边的声音又是何方神圣？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切的一切，究竟是因何而起，又将通向怎样的未来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/bf5af32e969ca96419ec941cd72e53fb.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span>您不光可以通过战斗提升队员的等级，进而学习越来越强大的技能；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且还可以通过转职系统，将队员们培养成您需要的样子，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进而在战斗中获得巨大的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，您可以在冒险的过程中选择与不同的女主角培养感情，而您做出的选择将会引导您进入不同的展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/961f927be469af5345bbea155da8e913.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/7b52fb87780a55b229d015f43b6357bc.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/e7cfeeffb11fa499b91f8efba4f39794.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/4142f472a0bc9777c2aa8cde7fe3c8bf.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>经典的角色扮演游戏体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了要让角色们在战斗中积累经验，收集装备和道具之外，您还需要让角色们在合适的时机做出合适的选择，推动剧情发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>妙趣横生的转职系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每名角色都可以选择专精于不同的能力，进而成长为各具特色的职业！用这些独特的能力消灭胆敢挡在他们面前的敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可供探索的奇幻世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您于大陆的各处游走，推动主线剧情的进展的同时，您也可以忙里偷闲，完成一些有趣的支线任务，让您的冒险生活更加丰富多彩。</p>",
